Unlike many newsletters, the Weekly Thing is not constrained to a specific topic. Think of it as a path of discovery in technology that evolves and changes. Some topics will come up regularly because they are principles that I care about deeply: leadership, privacy, productivity, and more. A friend once called the Weekly Thing a “direct feed from Jamie’s brain.” Another referred to the Weekly Thing as having a weekly coffee with an exciting friend and diving deep into different topics.
